My unsponsored hair wash routine:

Comment “link” to get direct link of products I have used & my recommendations ✨

1️⃣ Glycolic Acid – I keep it on my scalp for 10-15 minutes to break down buildup since I have an oily scalp. ( please don’t keep it on for more than 20 minutes) 

2️⃣ Shampoo & Conditioner – Using a paraben and sulfate-free set to keep my hair clean without harsh stuff.

3️⃣ Hair Mask – Leave this on for at least 5 minutes

4️⃣ Body Wash – I use Dove’s salicylic acid wash because it works well for me.

5️⃣ Hair Serum – Applied to damp hair, then I let it air dry.
